<h2 id="使用aria2-进行下载">使用Aria2 进行下载</h2>

<h3 id="windows">Windows</h3>

<h3 id="mac和linux">Mac和Linux</h3>

<p>使用下载工具将Aria2下载完毕</p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">apt-get install aria2c</code></p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">brew install aria2c</code></p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pacman -S aria2c</code></p>

<p>在家目录下新建文件夹<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.aria2</code></p>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">mkdir ~/.aria2/</code></p>

<p>新建<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">aria2.session</code>
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">touch aria2.session</code></p>

<p>新建并配置 <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">aria2.conf</code></p>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>运行
<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">aria2c --enable-rpc --rpc-listen-all</code></p>
